(36, 'SEO ALL cource', '<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">Crawler</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">make indexes and store in db.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Ranking done by:</span>&nbsp;organing search or using ads(pay per click)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">types of SEO:</span>&nbsp;on page SEO (coding) &amp; off page SEO (link building)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">traffic on google</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">by Search</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">social</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">direct</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">refferal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">Keywords (words that are liked by users)</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">short tail keywords: &lt;3 words ie phone</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">long tail keywords: ie phone prices in lahore</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">google index websites upto 4 levels ie HOME/products/new/branded</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">use unlimited pages but unique content</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">length of content like google but not people (so use bullets etc)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">Finding keywords</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"../../../MITcontent/www.ads.google.com\">www.ads.google.com</a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">For one page use &lt;=12 keywords &amp; unique for all pages</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ie for Garments store &gt;&gt; gents garment,ladies garment,kids garment.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Other Tools:</span>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"../../../MITcontent/\">market samurai</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"which keywords is more used now days\" href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/\">www.trends.google.com/trends/</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">check list (200+ factors for on page SEO)</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"list-group\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding-left: 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125); border-top-left-radius: 0.25rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.25rem;\">is your Home page contain all info+light weight</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Meta tags , title (60 charters), description (&lt;=150 char) ,</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">is all content is inside body ,content &gt;=500 words</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">use proper sentences,spellings, and related data (ie phone &rarr; price,lahore,screen etc)</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Proper keywords density, use &lt;=3% keywords, check online&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://www.prepostseo.com/keyword-density-checker\">www.prepostseo.com</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">use headings h1,h6. H1 is picked by crawlers so its very important</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">use latent semantic index ie Java-&gt;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">iceland</span>language<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">coffee</span>&nbsp;Google use LSI to find data</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Images:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: red;\">&lt;=100kb,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: green;\">alt tag (v imp),</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: blue;\">title tag,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: orange;\">figurecaption attribute,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: red;\">image name must be as keywords</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\" title=\"exit web page instantly by user\">reduce Bounce Rate</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\" title=\"collection of all urls+images+posts\">sitemap:</span>&nbsp;Make sitemap and submit to google console,online html,xmlsitemap&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://www.xml-sitemaps.com/\">www.xml-sitemaps.com/</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">use readable urls ie abc.com/AliResult not use abc.com/12.php</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">try to Make approximatly your web online 24/360, https://www.uptrends.com/ to web moniter</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">External Links</span>&nbsp;use good external links, ie wikipedia,000webhost.</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">use BreadCrumbs (URL &amp; page) ie a.com/products/iphone_SE , Home/products/iphone_SE</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Recency:</span>&nbsp;update content daily,weekly etc. so google crawler crawl data.</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Use good TLD&nbsp;</span>small+descriptive+keywords contain,old domain</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">use better design + lightweight ie shopify, stripe</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">is load speed is ok for mobile &amp; desktop,check online page speed&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/\">developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">check Responsiveness,use accelrated mobile pages (a new language) for high speed.&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://search.google.com/test/mobile-friendly\">google tester for responsiveness</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://validator.ampproject.org/\">amp validator</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Use schema Tags to show extra information ie price,rating,profile on searching google.&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: red;\">Schema</span>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://schema.org/\">schema.org/</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: green;\">Schema genrator</span>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://technicalseo.com/tools/\">technicalseo.com</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: orange;\">verify schema tags in website</span>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://search.google.com/structured-data/testing-tool/u/0/\">structure data testing tool</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Robots.txt</span>&nbsp;Dissallow pages from crawling and use to show sitemap.Make Robots.txt in parent directory. online Robots.txt make&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://tools.seobook.com/robots-txt/generator/\">tools.seobook.com</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Page Duplications,</span>&nbsp;a crawler think\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">a.com/a.php not equal to a.com/a.php?id=0</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">www.a.com not equal to a.com</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">http://a.com not equal to https://a.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nthis will show same content but these are different links</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Page Duplications solutions.</span>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">use canonical tags in head tells to Crawler that this page is copy of another(given) page. ie &lt;head rel=\"canonical\" href=\"rizi.com\"&gt; Now google cant crawl this page</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Redirection: use .htaccess file that works on current and its child dirctories. online htaccess genrate&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://htaccessredirect.net/\">www.htaccessredirect.net</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Broken Links, if assets deleted, its cant removed from Google index, so use 301 redirection for old to new links.&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"check broken links\" href=\"https://validator.w3.org/\">www.validator.w3.org</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"check broken links\" href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/\">www.google.com/webmasters/</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Open Graphs</span>&nbsp;to genrate preview for Facebook,twitter,insta etc.&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"facebook open graph\" href=\"https://smallseotools.com/\">www.smallseotools.com/</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://metatags.io/\">www.metatags.io/</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125); border-bottom-right-radius: 0.25rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.25rem;\">Install SSL Certificates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">Off page SEO</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"list-group\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding-left: 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125); border-top-left-radius: 0.25rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.25rem;\">When google comes from other websites it with give you more ranking, if other website is better it will give good marks.we will get links by\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Nature</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Out Reach (convince)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Non editorial (comment your link in other webs).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">NO follow links: That are not ranked by google. add rel=\"nofollow\" in anchor tags</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Register yourself in Google Business</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125); border-bottom-right-radius: 0.25rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.25rem;\">Use maps using Google Business (local SEO)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.75rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">Others</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"list-group\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding-left: 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125); border-top-left-radius: 0.25rem; border-top-right-radius: 0.25rem;\">SEO Quacke extention for chrome</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Use GOOGLE Light House for audit of your website (inspect element)</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">w3.org use for standard html, w3c validation</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Enable google analytics for testing SEO</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">_ make on youtube, underscore used for pre keywords suggestions.</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: -1px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);\">Multilanguage Website: Make different pages for different languages</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-group-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125); border-bottom-right-radius: 0.25rem; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.25rem;\">Multi Region websites: ie if 1000 items on a page, in pak only 30 is valid. then make two pages and add &lt;link rel=\"alternate href=\"\" hreflang=\"\"&gt;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">We just optamize web pages ,ranking done by Crawler</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">amazone has bad SEO,</p>', 8, '2020-02-24 15:28:00');
