(227, '.htaccess custom file open by default,custom error pages,response headers', '<h5><strong>1.htaccess file work on current folder and all sub folders.Apche check first htaccess file in every directory then&nbsp;</strong></h5>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>DirectoryIndex index2.php index.php index.html </code></pre>\r\n<p>This Directive will make Apache look first index2.php,then index.pnp then index.html</p>\r\n<p>put .htaccess,index.php,index.html,index2.php in same directory.</p>\r\n<h5><strong>2.error pages</strong></h5>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>errorDocument 400 http://localhost/htaccess/err_400.html\r\nerrorDocument 401 http://localhost/htaccess/err_401.html\r\nerrorDocument 404 http://localhost/htaccees/404error.html\r\nerrorDocument 500 http://localhost/htaccess/err_500.html</code></pre>\r\n<p>if any error occured, these pages displayed.</p>\r\n<h5><strong>3.Authentication</strong></h5>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>RewriteEngine On\r\nAuthType Basic\r\nAuthName \"Password Required\"\r\nAuthUserFile .httpass\r\nRequire valid-user</code></pre>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>make htaccess file and paste above code</li>\r\n<li>Make .httpass file and paste this code <span style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #ced4d9;\">rizi:12345</span></li>\r\n<li>make index.php and paste any data</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">now access file using localhost/htaccess/index.php</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">4.Add header in responce of every request</span></strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>Header add X-HeaderName \"Rizwan\"\r\nHeader add X-HeaderName2 \"shan\"</code></pre>', 1, '2020-04-15 13:13:03'),
(228, '$_SERVER[\'HTTP_REFERER\'] find where user come from', '<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>if(isset($_SERVER[\'HTTP_REFERER\'])) {\r\n    echo $_SERVER[\'HTTP_REFERER\'];\r\n}</code></pre>', 1, '2020-04-17 09:58:59'),
(229, 'change attributes of files using cmd.', '<p>ATTRIB [-|+] R|S|H filename /s /d</p>', 3, '2020-04-18 12:55:33'),
(230, 'Static Sections in your theme ||shopify', '<p><strong>1.Creating a static section in your Shopify theme</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Create a section and add it into&nbsp; layout,or liquid templates as <span style=\"background-color: #f4f6f8; color: #212b35; font-family: monospace; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\">{% section \'text\' %}</span></li>\r\n<li>A section contain schema, javascript or css</li>\r\n<li>I created a section text.liquid inside sections folder.</li>\r\n<li>Variables created outside sections are not available within sections.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>text.liquid</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;div id=\"textsection\"&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=\"simpletext\"&gt;\r\n    &lt;h1&gt; {{ section.settings.text-box }} &lt;/h1&gt;\r\n    &lt;h3&gt; {{ section.settings.text }} &lt;/h3&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n{% schema %}\r\n  {\r\n    \"name\": \"Text Box\",\r\n    \"settings\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"id\": \"text-box\",\r\n        \"type\": \"text\",\r\n        \"label\": \"Heading\",\r\n        \"default\": \"Title\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"id\": \"text\",\r\n        \"type\": \"richtext\",\r\n        \"label\": \"Add custom text below\",\r\n        \"default\": \"&lt;p&gt;Add your text here&lt;/p&gt;\"\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n{% endschema %}\r\n\r\n{% stylesheet %}\r\n{% endstylesheet %}\r\n\r\n{% javascript %}\r\n{% endjavascript %}</code></pre>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">text,text-box,image_picker, radio, video_url, and font. are some types.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>id refers to the Liquid tag being defined,</li>\r\n<li>type is kind of output</li>\r\n<li>label is defining a name for this output,</li>\r\n<li>and default is assigning a placeholder</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Note: We can\'t change positions of static sections.</p>', 6, '2020-04-19 13:24:48'),
(231, 'Dynamic Sections and blocks in your theme ||shopify', '<ul>\r\n<li>when a <strong>Preset</strong> is added it means we can access its block using add action button dynamically in theme editoe</li>\r\n<li><strong>Blocks</strong> are dynamic settings for section ie add, remove, modify texts</li>\r\n<li>Dynamic sections can be moved into different positions on the page using drag and drop.</li>\r\n<li>Add presets to the section file to make it dynamic</li>\r\n<li>name and a category must added to blocks</li>\r\n<li>we can and dynamic section to home page only up to 25</li>\r\n<li>No need to add section, it will auto available due to&nbsp; &nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; color: #5c6ac4; text-decoration-skip-ink: auto; border-bottom: none; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://shopify.dev/docs/themes/liquid/reference/objects#content_for_index\"><code class=\"text-highlight text-highlight--grey\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Lucida Console\', monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; display: inline; padding: 0.5px 5px 2px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #f4f6f8; border: 1px solid #c4cdd5;\">content_for_index</code></a>&nbsp; in index.liquid or theme.liquid</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Dynamic sections</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;div id=\"section-cta\"&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt;\r\n    &lt;h3&gt; {{ section.settings.text-box }} &lt;/h3&gt;\r\n    &lt;a href=\"{{ section.settings.link }}\" class=\"btn btn--cta\"&gt;{{ section.settings.linktext }}&lt;/a&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n{% schema %}\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Call to action\",\r\n  \"settings\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"id\": \"text-box\",\r\n      \"type\": \"text\",\r\n      \"label\": \"Heading\",\r\n      \"default\": \"Title\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"id\": \"link\",\r\n      \"type\": \"url\",\r\n      \"label\": \"Button link\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"id\": \"linktext\",\r\n      \"type\": \"text\",\r\n      \"label\": \"Button text\",\r\n      \"default\": \"Click here\"\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"presets\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"name\": \"Call to Action\",\r\n      \"category\": \"CTA button\"\r\n    }\r\n  ]\r\n}\r\n{% endschema %}\r\n\r\n{% stylesheet %}\r\n{% endstylesheet %}\r\n\r\n{% javascript %}\r\n{% endjavascript %}</code></pre>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>BLOCKS</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;hr&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=\"section-cta\"&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=\"section-header text-center\"&gt;\r\n    &lt;h3&gt; {{ section.settings.text-box }} &lt;/h3&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n  {% for block in section.blocks %}  \r\n  &lt;div class=\"btn\" id=\"call-to-action\"&gt;   \r\n    &lt;a href=\"{{ block.settings.link }}\" class=\"btn\"&gt;{{ block.settings.linktext }}&lt;/a&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt; \r\n  {% endfor %}\r\n\r\n&lt;/div&gt;  \r\n&lt;hr&gt;\r\n{% schema %}\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"CTA Blocks\",\r\n	\"max_blocks\": 3,\r\n  \"settings\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"id\": \"text-box\",\r\n      \"type\": \"text\",\r\n      \"label\": \"Heading\",\r\n      \"default\": \"Title\"\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"blocks\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"type\": \"select\",\r\n      \"name\": \"Add Button\",\r\n      \"settings\": [\r\n        {\r\n          \"id\": \"link\",\r\n          \"type\": \"url\",\r\n       		\"label\": \"Button link\"\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          \"id\": \"linktext\",\r\n          \"type\": \"text\",\r\n          \"label\": \"Button text\",\r\n          \"default\": \"Click here\"\r\n        }\r\n      ]\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"presets\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"name\": \"Call to Action Blocks\",\r\n      \"category\": \"CTA button\",\r\n      \"blocks\": [\r\n        { \r\n          \"type\": \"select\"\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          \"type\": \"select\"\r\n        }\r\n      ]\r\n    }\r\n  ]\r\n}\r\n{% endschema %}\r\n\r\n{% stylesheet %}\r\n{% endstylesheet %}\r\n\r\n{% javascript %}\r\n{% endjavascript %}</code></pre>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Access blocks links using loop</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>{% for block in section.blocks %}\r\n  &lt;div class=\"btn\" id=\"call-to-action\"&gt;   \r\n    &lt;a href=\"{{ block.settings.link }}\" class=\"btn\"&gt;{{ block.settings.linktext }}&lt;/a&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt; \r\n{% endfor %}</code></pre>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>EXAMPLES:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt;SIMPLE SYNTAX IMAGE SLIDER</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>{% if section.settings.title != blank %}\r\n  &lt;h3&gt;{{section.settings.title}}&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n{% endif %}\r\n{% for block in section.blocks %}\r\n  &lt;p&gt; \r\n     {%if  forloop.index0 == 0 %} &lt;h4&gt;first&lt;/h4&gt; {%endif%}\r\n  &lt;/p&gt;\r\n{% endfor %}\r\n  {% for block in section.blocks %}\r\n          &lt;img src=\"{{ block.settings.image | img_url:\'400x400\' }}\"&gt;\r\n            &lt;h5&gt; {{ block.settings.title }} &lt;/h5&gt;\r\n  {% endfor %}\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n{% schema %}\r\n  {\r\n    \"name\": \"new slider\",\r\n    \"max_blocks\": 10,\r\n    \"settings\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"type\": \"header\",\r\n        \"content\": \"new image slider\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"type\": \"text\",\r\n        \"id\": \"title\",\r\n        \"label\": \"Heading\",\r\n        \"default\": \"Slider title\"\r\n      }],\r\n\r\n    \"blocks\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"type\": \"image\",\r\n        \"name\": \"Image\",\r\n        \"settings\": [\r\n          {\r\n            \"type\": \"image_picker\",\r\n            \"id\": \"image\",\r\n            \"label\": \"Image\"\r\n          },\r\n          {\r\n            \"type\": \"text\",\r\n            \"id\": \"title\",\r\n            \"label\": \"Image title\"\r\n          }]}],\r\n\r\n    \"presets\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"name\": \"new Image slider by Rizi\",\r\n        \"category\": \"Image\"\r\n      }]}\r\n{% endschema %}</code></pre>\r\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt;Just Add slider_bs4.liquid to sections folder to use bootstrap 4 slider.</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;section class=\"image-slider\"&gt;\r\n\r\n    {% if section.settings.title != blank %}\r\n        &lt;h3 class=\"h3 text-center\"&gt;\r\n            {{section.settings.title}}\r\n        &lt;/h3&gt;\r\n    {% endif %}\r\n\r\n    &lt;div class=\"bd-example\"&gt;\r\n            &lt;div id=\"carouselExampleCaptions\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\"&gt;\r\n              &lt;ol class=\"carousel-indicators\"&gt;\r\n                  {% for block in section.blocks %}\r\n                    &lt;li data-target=\"#carouselExampleCaptions\" data-slide-to=\"{{forloop.index0}}\" {%if  forloop.index0 == 0 %} class=\"active\"{%endif%}&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n                {% endfor %}\r\n              &lt;/ol&gt;\r\n              &lt;div class=\"carousel-inner\"&gt;\r\n\r\n                    {% for block in section.blocks %}\r\n\r\n                        &lt;div class=\"carousel-item {% if forloop.first %} active {%endif%}\"&gt;\r\n                            &lt;img src=\"{{ block.settings.image | img_url:\'master\' }}\" class=\"d-block w-100\" alt=\"...\"&gt;\r\n                            &lt;div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\"&gt;\r\n                              &lt;h5&gt; {{ block.settings.title }} &lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n                            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n                    {% endfor %}\r\n\r\n\r\n              &lt;/div&gt;\r\n              &lt;a class=\"carousel-control-prev\" href=\"#carouselExampleCaptions\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;span class=\"carousel-control-prev-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                &lt;span class=\"sr-only\"&gt;Previous&lt;/span&gt;\r\n              &lt;/a&gt;\r\n              &lt;a class=\"carousel-control-next\" href=\"#carouselExampleCaptions\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\"&gt;\r\n                &lt;span class=\"carousel-control-next-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n                &lt;span class=\"sr-only\"&gt;Next&lt;/span&gt;\r\n              &lt;/a&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n\r\n{% schema %}\r\n  {\r\n    \"name\": \"Image Slider\",\r\n    \"max_blocks\": 10,\r\n    \"settings\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"type\": \"header\",\r\n        \"content\": \"Image Slider\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"type\": \"text\",\r\n        \"id\": \"title\",\r\n        \"label\": \"Heading\",\r\n        \"default\": \"Slider title\"\r\n      }\r\n    ],\r\n\r\n    \"blocks\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"type\": \"image\",\r\n        \"name\": \"Image\",\r\n        \"settings\": [\r\n          {\r\n            \"type\": \"image_picker\",\r\n            \"id\": \"image\",\r\n            \"label\": \"Image\"\r\n          },\r\n          {\r\n            \"type\": \"text\",\r\n            \"id\": \"title\",\r\n            \"label\": \"Image title\"\r\n          }\r\n        ]\r\n      }\r\n    ],\r\n\r\n    \"presets\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"name\": \"Image Slider\",\r\n        \"category\": \"Image\"\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n{% endschema %}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 6, '2020-04-19 13:30:56');
