(232, '{% schema %} tag ||shopify', '<ul>\r\n<li>Each section can have a single schema tag, and schema tags must contain valid JSON.</li>\r\n<li>Goto section&gt;create file.liquid &gt;make schema as below</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>A shema tag contain following properties.</p>\r\n<p><strong>name: </strong>Name of schema inside section</p>\r\n<p><strong>class: </strong>css class added to that wrapper</p>\r\n<p><strong>tag: </strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; color: #212b35; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">tag of the section\'s ie </span><span style=\"color: #212b35; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif;\">article,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #212b35; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif;\">aside,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #212b35; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: #2dc26b;\">div</span>, </span><span style=\"color: #212b35; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif;\">footer,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #212b35; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif;\">header, </span><span style=\"color: #212b35; font-family: ShopifySans, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif;\">section</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>settings: </strong>settings of section</p>\r\n<p><strong>blocks:</strong> containers of settings and content which can be added, removed, and reordered within&nbsp; section.&nbsp; Block have name and type (both defined by developer)</p>\r\n<p><strong>max_blocks:</strong> maximum number of blocks per section (<span style=\"background-color: #2dc26b;\">unlimited by def</span>)</p>\r\n<p><strong>presets:</strong> each preset becomes a dynamic section a merchant: precet has name and category</p>\r\n<p><strong>locales:</strong> languages of a section</p>\r\n<p><strong>Loop with section blocks:</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>{% for block in section.blocks %}\r\n  &lt;div class=\"grid-item\" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}&gt;\r\n    {% case block.type %}\r\n    {% when \'text\' %}\r\n      {{ block.settings.content }}\r\n    {% when \'image\' %}\r\n      &lt;img src=\"{{ block.settings.image | img_url }}\"&gt;\r\n    {% endcase %}\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n{% endfor %}</code></pre>', 6, '2020-04-19 18:17:33'),
